cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use austrata in your work, please cite it using these metadata."
title: austrata
abstract: >-
  A Python package for accessing Geoscience Australia open data (boreholes via
  GeoServer OGC WFS and the Hydrogeology of Australia via ArcGIS REST) and the
  Bureau of Meteorology NGIS state cores, with a provenance-aware local cache.
type: software
authors:
